branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The VZM series is a 5 port mechanical valve. It is compact in design with a large flow capacity (VZM400 Cv 0.55, VZM500 Cv 0.6). The VZM is available in a metal or rubber spool style, with a variety of actuator choices and optional external pilot.
&lt;/p&gt;

branchCategory.bullets:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluid: air, inert gas&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating pressure: 0.15 to 0.7MPa&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ambient and fluid temp: -5&#xb0; to 60&#xb0;C (no freezing)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective area (Cv): 0.6&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thread: NPT&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Port size: main valve 1/8, pilot valve (EXH) M5x0.8&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

